The '''''Thyfonian''''' was a modified [[Lambda-class T-4a shuttle/Legends|''Lambda''-class T-4a shuttle]]. It had high capacity [[Deflector shield generator/Legends|shield generators]] and upgraded laser cannons. It was to be [[Fliry Vorru]]'s private escape shuttle, however [[Ysanne Isard]] commandeered it to be her private escape shuttle during the final stages of the [[Battle of Thyferra]]. The Thyfonian was destroyed during the battle by [[Tycho Celchu/Legends|Tycho Celchu]] who was acting on sensor data provided by [[Corran Horn/Legends|Corran Horn]].

